## Pipeline Scripts (9 Stages)
1. `python 1_extract/sap_package_downloader.py /ZSAMPLE/MAIN` - Extract from SAP
2. `python 2_map_skills/scan_sample_pkg.py` - Syntax scan + FM classify
3. `python 2_map_skills/migrate_sample_pkg.py` - Pass 1: 14 regex transforms
4. `python 2_map_skills/deep_migrate_sample_pkg.py` - Pass 2: complex patterns
5. `python 2_map_skills/java_abap_mapper.py` - Unified skill mapping engine
6. `python 2_map_skills/twin_discovery_sample_pkg.py` - Semantic twin discovery
7. `python 2_map_skills/threeway_mapper.py` - 3-way mapping + CRV
8. `python 3_rag/index_zsample_all.py` - Index all knowledge to ChromaDB
9. `python 3_rag/rag_query_api.py "query"` - Query RAG

